quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  11,112,"Dúró ṣinṣin gẹ́gẹ́ bí A ṣe pa ìwọ àti ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá rónú pìwàdà pẹ̀lú rẹ láṣẹ. Ẹ má ṣe tayọ ẹnu-ààlà. Dájúdájú Òun ni Olùríran nípa ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́."
  11,113,"Ẹ má ṣe tẹ̀ sọ́dọ̀ àwọn tó ṣàbòsí nítorí kí Iná má baà fọwọ́ bà yín. Kò sì níí sí àwọn aláàbò fún yín lẹ́yìn Allāhu. Lẹ́yìn náà, A ò níí ràn yín lọ́wọ́."
  11,114,"Kírun ní etí ọ̀sán méjèèjìàti ní abala kan nínú òru Dájúdájú àwọn iṣẹ́ rere ń pa àwọn iṣẹ́ aburú rẹ́. Ìyẹn ni ìrántí fún àwọn olùrántí (Allāhu). {1}",1:[Ìyẹn ni ìbẹ̀rẹ̀ ọ̀sán àti ìparí ọ̀sán. Ìbẹ̀rẹ̀ ọ̀sán dúró fún lílà al-fajr fún ìrun Subh. Ìparí ọ̀sán dúró fún ìrun Ṭḥuhr àti ‘Asr.]
  12,73,"Wọ́n sọ pé: “A fi Allāhu búra, dájúdájú ẹ mọ̀ pé a kò wá láti ṣèbàjẹ́ lórí ilẹ̀. Àti pé àwa kì í ṣe olè.”"
  12,74,"Wọ́n sọ pé: “Kí ni ẹ̀san (fún ẹni tí) ó jí i, tí (ó bá hàn pé) ẹ̀yin jẹ́ òpùrọ́?”"
  12,75,"Wọ́n sọ pé: “Ẹ̀san rẹ̀; ẹni tí wọ́n bá bá a nínú ẹrù rẹ̀, òun náà ni ẹ̀san rẹ̀. Báyẹn ni àwa ṣe ń san àwọn alábòsí ní ẹ̀san (ní ọ̀dọ̀ tiwa).”1 {1}",1:[Nínú òfin tí Allāhu gbékalẹ̀ lórí olè ní àsìkò Ànábì Ya'ƙūb - kí ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - ni pé, tí ọwọ́ bá tẹ olè, wọ́n máa fà á lé olóhun lọ́wọ́, ó sì máa sọ ọ́ di ẹrú rẹ̀. Àmọ́ ní àsìkò Ànábì tiwa - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -, ọrùn ọwọ́ olè ni wọ́n máa gé pẹ̀lú àwọn májẹ̀mu rẹ̀.]
  13,40,"Ó ṣeé ṣe kí Á fi apá kan èyí tí A ṣe ní ìlérí fún wọn hàn ọ́ tàbí kí Á ti gba ẹ̀mí rẹ (ṣíwájú àsìkò náà), ìkéde (ẹ̀sìn) nìkan ni ojúṣe tìrẹ, ìṣírò-iṣẹ́ sì ni tiWa."
  13,41,"Ṣé wọn kò wòye pé dájúdájú À ń dé sórí ilẹ̀, À ń dín in kù (mọ́ àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ lọ́wọ́) láti àwọn eteetí ìlú (wọ inú ìlú nípa fífún àwọn mùsùlùmí ní ìṣẹ́gun lórí wọn)? Allāhu l’Ó ń ṣe ìdájọ́. Kò sí ẹnì kan tí ó lè dá ìdájọ́ Rẹ̀ padà (fún Un). Òun sì ni Olùyára níbi ìṣírò-iṣẹ́."
  13,42,"Dájúdájú àwọn tó ṣíwájú wọn déte. Ti Allāhu sì ni gbogbo ète pátápátá.Ó mọ ohun tí ẹ̀mí kọ̀ọ̀kan ń ṣe níṣẹ́. Àti pé àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ ń bọ̀ wá mọ ẹni tí àtubọ̀tán Ilé (rere) wà fún. {1}",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Baƙọrah; 2:15.]
  14,19,"Ṣé o kò wòye pé dájúdájú Allāhu l’Ó ṣẹ̀dá àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ pẹ̀lú òdodo? Tí Ó bá fẹ́, Ó máa ko yín kúrò. Ó sì máa mú ẹ̀dá titun wá."
  14,20,"Ìyẹn kò sì lè dá Allāhu lágara."
  14,21,"Gbogbo ẹ̀dá sì máa jáde sọ́dọ̀ Allāhu (lọ́jọ́ Àjíǹde). Nígbà náà, àwọn aláìlágbára yóò wí fún àwọn tó ṣègbéraga pé: “Dájúdájú àwa jẹ́ ọmọlẹ́yìn fún yín, ǹjẹ́ ẹ̀yin lè gbé n̄ǹkan kan kúrò fún wa nínú ìyà Allāhu?” Wọn yóò wí pé: “Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé Allāhu tọ́ wa sọ́nà ni, àwa ìbá tọ yín sọ́nà. Bákan náà sì ni fún wa, yálà a káyà sókè tàbí a ṣàtẹ̀mọ́ra (ìyà); kò sí ibùsásí kan fún wa.”"